title: Are Song Lyrics Real? This Celeb Is Saying Another Rapper Is Lying About Being Shot
description:
Can you believe what you hear in songs? Are lyrics fictional or based off real life...or both? Moe weighs in as one MAJOR rapper is calling out another rapper, saying she was lying about being shot. And he's not the first one to come for her.
